//000000086400a:4:{i:0;a:10:{s:2:"id";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:12:"新手指南";s:5:"brief";s:0:"";s:3:"pid";s:1:"0";s:9:"is_effect";s:1:"1";s:9:"is_delete";s:1:"0";s:7:"type_id";s:1:"0";s:4:"sort";s:1:"1";s:8:"iconfont";s:8:"&#58887;";s:9:"help_list";a:8:{i:0;a:20:{s:2:"id";s:1:"3";s:5:"title";s:12:"常见问题";s:7:"content";s:34945:"<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、什么是夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">是一个“我为人人、人人为我”的新型互助购物平台。</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">将用户共同需求的商品分成若干等份，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">元即可支持</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">等份，当</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">件商品的所有等份都获得支持后，根据平台互助购物协议，此商品将归其中一位支持者所有。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;">　　规则：</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　 （1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）依据市场价将每个商品分成若干等份，每份</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">元；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）每个用户可对</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">件商品支持</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">份或多份，每支持</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">份获得</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">个中奖码；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）当</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">件商品的所有份额都获得支持后，计算出</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">个“幸运</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">”，持有“幸运</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">”的支持者即拥有该商品。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;">　　计算方式：</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）以该商品最后支持时间为截至点，取全网最后</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">100</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">条支持时间记录；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）每条时间记录按时、分、秒、毫秒依次排列成一个数值；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）将</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">100</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">个数值之和除以商品总需支持份数后取余，加上</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">10000001</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">为计算结果。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、什么是</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">？如何产生？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">是您成功支持商品后获得的凭证，您每支持</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">等份即可获得一个</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">是随机发放的，比如一件</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3500</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">元的商品，那</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">则为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">10000001-10003500</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">打乱在系统中，您每支持一等份，便会获得随机发放的一个</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、幸运</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">和商品获得者是如何计算出来的？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　持有幸运</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">的支持者即获得该商品，幸运中奖码的计算方式：</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）以该商品最后支持时间为截至点，取全网最后</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">100</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">条支持时间记录；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）每条时间记录按时、分、秒、毫秒依次排列成一个数值；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）将</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">100</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">个数值之和除以商品总需支持份数后取余，加上</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">10000001</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">为计算结果。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">4</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、如何参与夺宝？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）注册账号</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　登录夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">完成注册；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）挑选商品</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　分类浏览或直接搜索商品，点击“立即夺宝</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">”；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）支付</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　通过在线支付平台充值后，支付</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">元即支持</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">等份，获得</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">个“中奖码”；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">4</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）揭晓获得者</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　当</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">件商品的所有等份都获得支持后，计算出</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">名商品获得者，夺宝联盟网</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">会通过手机短信或邮件通知商品获得者领取商品。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　 &nbsp; 注：</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）商品揭晓后您可登录“我的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">”查询详情，未获得商品的用户不会收到短信或邮件通知；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）商品揭晓后，请及时登录“我的</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝”完善个人资料，以便我们能够准确无误地为您配送商品；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）所有已揭晓商品均不给予退款。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">5</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、如何保证幸运中奖码一定会在</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">当中产生？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　根据“将</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">100</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">个数值之和除以商品总需支持份数后取余，加上</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">10000001</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">为计算结果”的计算规则；</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">由于余数的区间为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">0</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">≤余数＜除数，则</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">0</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">≤余数＜本商品总需支持份数；</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">那么必定：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">0</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">＜余数</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">+10000001</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">≤商品总需支持份数，因此“余数</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">+ 10000001</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">”的结果肯定是在大家支持商品后获得的</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">当中的。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">6</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、参与夺宝后，什么时候揭晓商品？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">平台上的商品均是所有等份都获得支持后，倒计时</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">分钟揭晓结果。成功支持商品后，请您持续关注</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">7</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、三分钟倒计时是什么意思？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　在商品的最后一等份获得支持后，幸运</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">中奖码</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">就被计算出来了。最后三分钟倒计时，对揭晓结果没有任何影响。三分钟倒计时，只是为了聚拢人气，让更多夺友，共同见证商品获得者的幸运时刻。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">8</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、一些商品中标注的十年使用权是什么意思？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　由于一些商品价值过高，无使用权标注，是无法通过</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">平台互助购物模式销售的，而机器和其它商品使用</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">10</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">年后几乎已不能使用，是不会收回的。所以作使用权的标注，只是为了便于大家在</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">平台进行互助购物，不会对任何商品进行回收。根据</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">平台互助购物协议，一旦获得商品，所有权和使用权归商品获得者所有。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">9</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、如果我获得了商品，怎么通知我？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　当您成为商品获得者，系统会通过短信或邮件通知您。请您注意查看短信和邮件，保持手机和邮箱能正常使用。如未绑定手机号，请您务必要及时绑定哦，否则在您获得商品时，只能通过邮件接收消息或登录</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">官网查询哦。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">10</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、怎么知道我有没有获得商品？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　商品揭晓后，您可以进入“我的夺宝</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">-</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">获得的商品”查询揭晓情况。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">11</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、获得商品后我该做什么？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　获得商品之后请前往“我的夺宝</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">-</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">获得的商品”填写真实有效的收货地址，我们会在您提交收货地址后的第一时间为您安排发货。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">12</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、填写收货地址需要注意哪些？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　普通类商品：请务必填写真实有效的收货人、收货地址、联系电话等，以便商品顺利为您送达；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　定制类商品：戒指、鞋子、服饰等不支持换货，请确认规格后再提交；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　应时类商品：月饼、水果、生鲜等过期后无法换货，请及时提交收货信息；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　特殊类商品：汽车、房产、跨境商品等请务必提交真实有效的姓名、身份证件等信息，一旦审核通过，不可再更改；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　其他商品特殊要求。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">13</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、获得商品后，还需要支付其他费用吗？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　不需要支付其他任何费用。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">14</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、获得的商品可以兑现吗？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　不支持兑现。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">15</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、为什么我参与这么久，都没有获得商品呢？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　在</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">网上，任何人对商品的支持时间都会影响最终的结果，这是谁都无法控制的哦，因此建议大家理性参与。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">16</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、我参与夺宝后能申请退款吗？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　假设您参与的商品超过</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">天未获得所有支持，您可以申请退款，但</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">天内获得所有支持，则不支持退款哦。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">17</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、没有获得商品，可以申请退款吗？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:11pt;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" microsoft="" yahei",="" simhei,="" sans-serif;font-size:14px;"="" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　除超过</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">天“未获得所有支持”的商品可申请退款外，其余商品均不支持退款哦，因为您参与的款项已用于支持幸运获得者了。</span></p>
