</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">二</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">花呗、信用卡充值资金，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">7</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">日后申请提现，第一次提现金额低于</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2000</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">则免费，第二次收取</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1%</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">手续费，第三次开始收取百分之</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">5%</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">手续费，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">24</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">小时内到账；</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">2.</span></b></span></span><span style="font-family:arial;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">充值赠送</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">：</span></b><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">（</span></span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">工作日</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">9:00-17:00</span><b><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">）</span></b><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">首冲</span></font>100<font face="宋体"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">送</span></font><font face="Arial"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">20</span></font></span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">现金</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:10.5pt;"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">红包，联系在线客服</span></font></span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">领取。非推广商以及</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:10.5pt;"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">花呗、信用卡充值赠送只能消费不能提现</span></font></span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">；白银推广商：月提现总额</span></font>5000<font face="宋体"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">；黄金推广商月提现总额</span></font><font face="Arial"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span></font><font face="宋体"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">万；钻石推广商月提现总额</span></font><font face="Arial"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">5</span></font><font face="宋体"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">万；七日后可申请提现；</span></font></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:10.5pt;"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">3.</span></b></span></span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">推广奖</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">：</span></b>奖励满七天后</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">的第一个工作日</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">可申请提现</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">500</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">起提，收取</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2%</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">手续费。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">24</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">小时内到账；</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">4.</span></span><span style="font-family:arial;"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">管理奖</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:arial;">：</span></span></b><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">奖励满七天后的第一个工作日可申请提现</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2000</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">起提，收取</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2%</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">手续费，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">24</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">小时内到账。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:arial, sans-serif;"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">注：若发现违反相关金融规定或法律，经核实，本公司有权冻结账户（如：信用卡、花呗套现；洗黑钱；大额资金非正常急进急出），其他未尽事宜以国家法律及相关规定为依据。</span></p>
";s:7:"cate_id";s:1:"1";s:11:"create_time";s:10:"1506629054";s:11:"update_time";s:10:"1508699962";s:12:"add_admin_id";s:1:"0";s:9:"is_effect";s:1:"1";s:7:"rel_url";s:0:"";s:15:"update_admin_id";s:1:"0";s:9:"is_delete";s:1:"0";s:11:"click_count";s:1:"0";s:4:"sort";s:2:"13";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:11:"seo_keyword";s:0:"";s:15:"seo_description";s:0:"";s:5:"uname";s:0:"";s:11:"notice_page";s:1:"0";s:9:"sub_title";s:0:"";s:5:"brief";s:0:"";}i:7;a:20:{s:2:"id";s:2:"21";s:5:"title";s:18:"了解夺宝联盟";s:7:"content";s:3433:"<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　夺宝联盟是一个“我为人人、人人为我”的新型互助购物平台。夺宝联盟将用户共同需求的商品分成若干等份，1元即可支持1等份，当1件商品的所有等份都获得支持后，根据平台互助购物协议，此商品将归其中一位支持者所有。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;">　　规则：</span></b></span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　1、依据市场价将每个商品分成若干等份，每份1元。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　2、每个用户可对1件商品支持1份或多份，每支持1份获得1个中奖码。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　3、当1件商品的所有份额都获得支持后，计算出1个“幸运中奖码”，持有“幸运中奖码”的支持者即拥有该商品。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　计算方式：</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　1、以该商品最后支持时间为截至点，取全网最后100条支持时间记录。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　2、每条时间记录按时、分、秒、毫秒依次排列成一个数值。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　3、将100个数值之和除以商品总需支持份数后取余，加上10000001为计算结果。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　流程：</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　1、挑选商品</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　分类浏览或直接搜索商品，点击“立即夺宝”。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;">2、支付1元</span></b></span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　通过在线支付平台，支付1元即支持1等份，获得1个“中奖码”。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;">3、揭晓获得者</span></b></span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　当1件商品的所有等份都获得支持后，计算出1名商品获得者，夺宝联盟网会通过手机短信或邮件通知您领取商品。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　注：</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(1) 商品揭晓后您可登录“我的夺宝记录”查询详情，未获得商品的用户不会收到短信或邮件通知；</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(2) 商品揭晓后，若您为商品获得者，请及时登录“我的幸运记录”完善个人资料，以便我们能够准确无误地为您配送商品；</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(3) 所有已揭晓商品均不予退款</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;">4、晒单分享</span></b></span></div>
<div><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　晒出您收到的商品实物图片甚至您的靓照，说出您的夺宝心得，让大家一起分享您的快乐。</span></div>
";s:7:"cate_id";s:1:"1";s:11:"create_time";s:10:"1506726419";s:11:"update_time";s:10:"1506726419";s:12:"add_admin_id";s:1:"0";s:9:"is_effect";s:1:"1";s:7:"rel_url";s:0:"";s:15:"update_admin_id";s:1:"0";s:9:"is_delete";s:1:"0";s:11:"click_count";s:1:"0";s:4:"sort";s:2:"20";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:11:"seo_keyword";s:0:"";s:15:"seo_description";s:0:"";s:5:"uname";s:0:"";s:11:"notice_page";s:1:"0";s:9:"sub_title";s:0:"";s:5:"brief";s:0:"";}}}i:1;a:10:{s:2:"id";s:1:"2";s:5:"title";s:12:"夺宝保障";s:5:"brief";s:0:"";s:3:"pid";s:1:"0";s:9:"is_effect";s:1:"1";s:9:"is_delete";s:1:"0";s:7:"type_id";s:1:"0";s:4:"sort";s:1:"2";s:8:"iconfont";s:8:"&#58906;";s:9:"help_list";a:1:{i:0;a:20:{s:2:"id";s:2:"20";s:5:"title";s:15:"账号和安全";s:7:"content";s:9654:"<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、如何注册</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">账号？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　登录</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">在登录页面点击注册，即可注册</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">账号。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、有哪些方式登录</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　使用夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">账号可直接登录</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、手机号或邮箱不用了，如何更换绑定手机号或邮箱？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　您可以拨打客服电话027-59260885</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">或联系在线客服，会有客服人员协助您处理。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">4</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、手机或邮箱收不到验证码怎么办？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(1)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">请检查手机是否安装了安全软件，开启了短信拦截功能；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(2)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">请检查邮箱的垃圾箱，某些邮箱会将验证邮件误判为垃圾邮件；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(3)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">如果以上操作都无法解决您的问题，请拨打客服电话027-</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">59260885</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">或联系在线客服，会有客服专员协助您处理。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">5</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、账号被盗怎么办？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　请勿将您的用户名和密码泄露给任何人哦。</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">绝不会向您索要密码或验证码。如果发现账号被盗，请第一时间修改密码。如不能登录也无法修改密码，请及时拨打客服电话</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">027-</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">59260885</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">或联系在线客服，会有客服人员协助您处理。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">6</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、忘记密码怎么办？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　登录</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">在登录页面点击“忘记密码”按钮，即可进行找回密码操作。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">7</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、账号被冻结了怎么办？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　请及时拨打客服电话</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">027-</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">59260885</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">或联系在线客服，会有客服人员协助您处理。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">8</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、郑重声明，</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">绝不会向您索要密码或验证码。以下行为均涉嫌诈骗，请广大</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">用户注意警惕并及时反馈！</span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(1)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">使用</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟LOGO</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">做为头像，冒充</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">官方工作人员，加好友、发送私信，以各种理由向您索要密码、验证码等账户信息；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(2)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">谎称可以挑选商品颜色、优先发货、获得指定商品；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(3)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">声称要缴纳“发货费”、“保护费”、“邮费”等才发货；</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(4)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">要求加</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">QQ</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">或微信，索要红包，承诺可以交钱合资、代投、代抽获得指定商品；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(5)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">谎称可以代充值并发送假冒的付款二维码、链接；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(6)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">发送大量虚假的获得商品通知短信或邮件，套取账户信息；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(7)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">谎称有内部员工、系统漏洞等，以获得特定商品为由，要求发送</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">QQ</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">红包、微信红包、私下交易等；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(8)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">声称有第三方或自己开发的夺宝辅助工具、软件，以能够预测、提前获知幸运夺宝码等理由收取使用费等；</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　(9)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">QQ</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">群、微信群或私信发送钓鱼网站、木马软件的链接等。</span></p>
