<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　我们会在您填写收货地址后</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">个工作日内为您安排发货。部分预售、定制或紧俏商品发货周期会相对延长哦，更多信息可拨打客服电话</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">027-</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">59260885</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">或联系在线客服进行咨询。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、商品发什么快递？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p><span times="" newroman";mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:zh-cn;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;"="" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　不同商品，不同收货地区，匹配不同快递为您发货。您可以留意订单详情，及时查看物流信</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">息。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、获得商品后想修改地址或收件人怎么办？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　在订单未确认前，您只需进入“获得的商品”，选择要修改地址的订单，点击左下角“修改”按钮，验证收货人手机号后即可输入新的收货信息。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">4</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、获得商品后可以挑选颜色或型号吗？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　以具体获得的商品为准，符合选色或型号要求的商品，在提交收货信息时，部分商品可以自行选择，如没有颜色或型号的选择，将会随机为您发货。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">5</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、获得商品后如果缺货怎么办？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　如果商品缺货，</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">客服人员会联系您调换网站其他商品；如果您不接受商品调换，可能需要等待较长时间哦。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">6</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、如何查看发货后的物流信息？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　商品发货后，登录</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">，可以查看最新的订单物流信息。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">7</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、为什么看不到物流信息？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　当天发出的商品，快递公司可能还未录入系统，建议您在第二天进行快递物流信息的查询。部分商品由于不支持直接查看物流信息，需要您手动复制快递单号，去对应的快递公司官网进行查询。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">8</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、商品尚未签收，但是不小心点了确认收货怎么办？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　您不必担心，误点了确认收货不影响商品的实际配送。请您保持收货电话畅通，注意查收商品就可以了。如有疑问，您可拨打客服电话027-</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">59260885</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">或联系在线客服进行咨询。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">9</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">、签收时需要注意哪些问题？</span></b><span lang="EN-US"><o :p=""></o></span></p>
<p><span times="" newroman";mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:zh-cn;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;"="" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">　　您在签收商品时请慎重，请尽量不要让人代签，并务必先仔细检查商品（外包装是否被开封、商品是否破损、配件是否缺失、功能是否正常等），确保无误后再签收，以免产生不必要的纠纷。若有任何疑问，请及时拨打客服电话反馈信息。若因您未仔细检查商品即签收后产生的纠纷，</span><span times="" newroman";mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:zh-cn;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;"="" style="font-family:arial;font-size:14px;">夺宝联盟概不负责，但我们一定会主动协助您处理。</span></p>
